{"tid":1850671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年輕內科護士：以前SARS是服務香港人，為何現在要用條命服務內地人？","createTime":"2020-01-29T16:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T18:39:00.000Z","uid":240448,"like":70,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4cabac9152ca840cb5cd9dbe68e5d6cdd875484e","tid":1850671,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:02:49.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】2003年本港爆發SARS，醫護同心抗疫拯救危城；2020年新型冠狀病毒襲港，醫護連日呼籲「封關抗疫」，否則罷工，昨日瑪嘉烈醫院及東區醫院共20名護士請假抗議。曾經歷SARS的兒科護士對港府控疫不力失望，表示若被編入照顧懷疑或確診患者的隊伍（dirty team）會辭職，<em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">「以前SARS是服務香港人，為何現在要用條命服務內地人？」</span></span></em>有年輕內科護士亦有意請辭，拒為港府「賣命」。<br />\n<br />\n瑪嘉烈東區昨20護士集體請假<br />\n<br />\n九龍西醫院聯網兒科護士Sandy（化名），曾經歷SARS，形容當年大家同心抗疫，即使醫管局初期對病毒一無所知、欠隔離設施、人手安排混亂等，都會體諒管理層。當時其部門約有50名護士，僅一人在加入dirty team前辭職，其他人都緊守崗位，若有同事染疫倒下，隨時由其他醫護頂上。<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">稱三分之一同事萌去意</span></span></em><br />\n<br />\n捱過SARS、每年流感高峰，Sandy從沒想過辭職，惟她不滿港府控疫措施滯後，甚至比澳門落後，<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">「早知涉新型冠狀病毒，（港府）等到湖北省暫停交通才禁湖北人入境，是沒有意思的」。她與同事均萌去意，稱其病房有三分之一護士表明，如要入dirty team會請辭，「一定是港府有問題才會這樣做，香港醫護不會隨便罷工」。</span></span></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n「不是怕死，是想逼政府做事」<br />\n<br />\n她說目前各病房護士均商討如何參與罷工，暫傾向請病假，但憂秋後算帳，「我們不是怕死，而是想逼政府做些事」。她又說，曾在醫院做小規模統計，13名護士中，10人拒入dirty team，「以前SARS是服務香港人，為何現在要用條命服務內地人？」她認為責任在政府，促全面關閉接壤內地的口岸、禁旅客經內地入境。<br />\n<br />\n本報獲悉東區醫院深切治療部昨有15名護士請假，該院內科護士Jason（化名）向本報透露，該批護士盼向港府施壓，要求全面實施對內地入境限制。Jason稱，醫院充斥擔憂及憤怒氣氛，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">「我個人對港府宣布局部封關不收貨，最擔心病毒源源不絕攻港，有帶病毒者潛伏社區，導致社區爆發」。</span></span><br />\n<br />\nJason說不想入dirty team，其病房三分之一護士有意請辭，包括資淺及資深的，<em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">「明白照顧病人是我們的天職，但不值得為政府送命」。他又說醫管局沒為dirty team醫護安排washout period（洗滌期），擔心立即返回原本病房會感染病人。<br />\n</span></span></em><br />\n瑪嘉烈醫院及東區醫院發言人昨證實有護士集體請病假，涉瑪嘉烈5名內科病房護士，東區有5名及10名深切治療部護士分別於早上和下午請病假，並說醫院已調配人手，病房服務維持正常。<br />\n<br />\n醫局：員工肩負重任 須緊守崗位<br />\n<br />\n醫管局昨透過人力資源應用程式發信息，稱全體員工都肩負重任，全力抗疫，假期後所有員工都須緊守崗位，感謝員工維持服務。對於不設washout period，醫管局發言人表示有既定感染控制指引及培訓，避免院內感染。<br />\n<br />\n明報記者<br />\n<br />\n（武漢肺炎）"},{"pid":"e8108e7f2daf6e4dcd072ccb567894ac6a6d556e","tid":1850671,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:03:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20200129/s00001/1580236180599/%e6%8b%92%e7%82%ba%e6%b8%af%e5%ba%9c%e8%b3%a3%e5%91%bd-%e8%ad%b7%e5%a3%ab-%e5%85%a5dirty-team%e6%9c%83%e8%be%ad%e8%81%b7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200129%2Fs00001%2F1580236180599%2F%25e6%258b%2592%25e7%2582%25ba%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%25ba%259c%25e8%25b3%25a3%25e5%2591%25bd-%25e8%25ad%25b7%25e5%25a3%25ab-%25e5%2585%25a5dirty-team%25e6%259c%2583%25e8%25be%25ad%25e8%2581%25b7&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=5314fa3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200129%2Fs00001%2F1580236180599%2F%25e6%258b%2592%25e7%2582%25ba%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%25ba%259c%25e8%25b3%25a3%25e5%2591%25bd-%25e8%25ad%25b7%25e5%25a3%25ab-%25e5%2585%25a5dirty-team%25e6%259c%2583%25e8%25be%25ad%25e8%2581%25b7&h=06802e49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20200129/s00001/1580236180599/%e6%8b%92%e7%82%ba%e6%b8%af%e5%ba%9c%e8%b3%a3%e5%91%bd-%e8%ad%b7%e5%a3%ab-%e5%85%a5dirty-team%e6%9c%83%e8%be%ad%e8%81%b7</a>"},{"pid":"282fdf6a251498d54d1e8e7487b1588fac308c20","tid":1850671,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:04:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7c7a26e0dc1125f30c8370edefe3bff7aaa88ee","tid":1850671,"uid":240448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:06:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y27LPp5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy27LPp5.jpg&h=4edbec9e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yvYK4Yr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyvYK4Yr.jpg&h=0eb1e630&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wq6s2K7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWq6s2K7.jpg&h=53074229&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9c66294232418a3533f7f497ff538bd3767ac02","tid":1850671,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:09:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"019fbb50c9a61dc2dd705458394aa5942cbfb0b6","tid":1850671,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:10:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01d16a871a6d3a79f3d373a4fa3d50cc7d7150b5","tid":1850671,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:11:18.000Z","msg":"G持清"},{"pid":"f4cb4a9fc3deda10bc4e4eab10e9cf98c6a0610f","tid":1850671,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:11:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b078d5183a857111cf022fd6e135294a5427f798","tid":1850671,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9005ca44d27ef66e4dfcf47d20b35ff1898f751a","tid":1850671,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:19:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b9d937fc4e1c477e0e5325b45bb6f609b76437d3","tid":1850671,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:19:56.000Z","msg":"吳三桂可恥！放晒的講滿州話匪入來！"},{"pid":"699953cdd444728e50ea2ab89bbbce0bf8ba1c61","tid":1850671,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:29:47.000Z","msg":"講得好 罷工啦"},{"pid":"e3fd0a4ccc58d95114c7881be8c81e307ef12a54","tid":1850671,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:30:01.000Z","msg":"今次肺炎絕對係喚醒港豬同狙擊藍絲最佳時機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850723</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2f6739084739ba67cfca6e55c5a09ec7c126d33d","tid":1850671,"uid":291526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:42:34.000Z","msg":"大陸人鬧咗我地半年「廢青暴徒」<br />\n而家要我地最珍貴嘅醫護去為佢地搏命？<br />\n罷佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b766c4badd459b352ea29abbe44bb9d558c9d8","tid":1850671,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東建國 香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廣東建國 香港獨立 港中區隔"},{"pid":"747cdee33e7d0340b25b55e8c547d954d73f7bea","tid":1850671,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:07:51.000Z","msg":"唔好撈啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f549e6f9c239b8b522c16b9180a0a0e8d13cdf","tid":1850671,"uid":335235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:22:51.000Z","msg":"好啱"},{"pid":"0d2c2ac2bdcc897e0ce098716470f2976e05d80f","tid":1850671,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:26:23.000Z","msg":"醫護手足 點可以因為一場本可以封關避免嘅病毒而賭上生命<br />\n我地仲未光復到香港啊..<br />\nbtw p牌求推一推... <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥  借刀殺人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850782</a>"},{"pid":"85aca1ef93206194eb090cb72395854c497fc3ea","tid":1850671,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:00:00.000Z","msg":"呢大半年<br />\n睇到港共點兇殘維穩<br />\n仲賣命要分擔罪孽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac776e613070d572305e14e36a781df48c562353","tid":1850671,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:00:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2caf163b1eae72d2bf24e523e2553297fe279863","tid":1850671,"uid":69746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:03:55.000Z","msg":"啱呀 一齊罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e8f4771b3beb19add0233a67cdd0181cc1826b","tid":1850671,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ubsLP7z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FubsLP7z.png&h=691270dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5bd324dd9a9cf22411a7e58fe043142a59d175e7","tid":1850671,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:38:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"021c8a1c00c047330201fa19b2b9ea2bb33df731","tid":1850671,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2caf163b1eae72d2bf24e523e2553297fe279863","tid":1850671,"uid":69746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:03:55.000Z","msg":"啱呀 一齊罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:39:00.000Z","msg":"要一齊罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}